name: Your Bish Therapist- Melissa Reich, MA

episodes.title: Twin Flames Universe: Cult or Spiritual Refuge?
episodes.description: Trigger warning: This episode contains discussion of cults, abuse (religious/spiritual, emotional, verbal and sexual), coercion around sexual orientation and gender identity/expression, discussion of gender dysphoria and trauma. This episode features direct quotes from victims and perpetrators; Listener discretion is advised. In this supersized season finale episode, YBT dives deep into the world of Twin Flames leaders Jeff and Shaleia Ayan. Information shared in the podcast was compiled from two documentaries, a podcast and several news articles. YBT synthesized all this content to bring you a full picture of the Twin Flames Universe. YBT discusses different types of cults, warning signs about whether a group is a cult and provides an extensive explanation of how and why people get sucked into cults. YBT shares FACTS based on research studies, science and psychology. Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
